reviewText: Exactly what I expected from a DVD!  I can watch these movies over and over again even though I'm quite a bit older than the first time I viewed them.
Too hokey for me.  I will be donating this soon, will not watch it again.
I have these movies before and I really enjoy them I was glad to get them both on one disc. I think they are both really good movies and I would recommend them

brings you back to the mid 90's. good movie to watch and enjoy for a good laugh. make it a movie night with this purchase.
